WEBVTT

00:00:00.253 --> 00:00:03.834
"Fruit"

00:00:04.417 --> 00:00:08.129
(Episode 4: Fog)

00:00:09.712 --> 00:00:10.866
Miss, Miss.

00:00:12.266 --> 00:00:13.266
Look.

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:15.566
Did I make this part too dark?

00:00:16.466 --> 00:00:18.633
Or do you think it can be darker?

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:23.600
It's dirty. Draw another one.

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:25.966
Ugh, Miss...

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:28.433
We're in class. Please be quiet.

00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:32.066
Okay...

00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:41.843
Miss, can you help me...

00:01:52.266 --> 00:01:54.600
Hey, did you get dumped?

00:01:54.966 --> 00:01:56.066
No.

00:01:56.666 --> 00:01:57.833
Don't talk nonsense.

00:02:15.533 --> 00:02:16.533
No.

00:02:17.700 --> 00:02:20.033
The doctor didn't say that.

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:21.337
Okay.

00:02:21.337 --> 00:02:23.167
Okay, I got it.

00:02:23.466 --> 00:02:25.366
Mmhmm.

00:02:26.166 --> 00:02:27.033
Okay.

00:02:32.307 --> 00:02:33.307
Miss...

00:02:38.766 --> 00:02:40.667
Class is starting.
Go back to your classroom.

00:02:48.365 --> 00:02:50.866
Why is she... so cold?

00:02:55.281 --> 00:02:56.800
I don't want to go back.

00:03:32.366 --> 00:03:33.266
Miss.

00:03:34.666 --> 00:03:35.700
Hmm?

00:03:42.402 --> 00:03:44.266
Why...

00:03:44.266 --> 00:03:46.033
did you ignore me today?

00:03:50.600 --> 00:03:51.700
I'm sorry.

00:03:52.900 --> 00:03:54.728
I was too harsh with you today.

00:04:04.102 --> 00:04:07.919
♪ Looking at you ♪

00:04:07.919 --> 00:04:13.336
♪ My heart starts to tense ♪

00:04:13.336 --> 00:04:16.518
♪ Its rhythm quickens ♪

00:04:16.518 --> 00:04:20.620
♪ Without my knowing ♪

00:04:20.620 --> 00:04:25.276
♪ Your gaze upon me ♪

00:04:25.276 --> 00:04:27.815
♪ In that strangeness ♪

00:04:27.815 --> 00:04:32.343
♪ I feel excitement rise ♪

00:04:34.544 --> 00:04:35.578
Wait!

00:04:40.533 --> 00:04:41.766
Were you dreaming?

00:04:42.133 --> 00:04:43.133
No.

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:45.297
Your face is so red.

00:04:45.298 --> 00:04:46.204
Is it?

00:04:47.466 --> 00:04:48.500
It's too hot.

00:04:51.500 --> 00:04:53.700
So hot. Don't you think it's stuffy today?

00:05:02.239 --> 00:05:03.239
Goodness.

00:05:04.636 --> 00:05:06.208
Why this kind of dream?

00:05:09.047 --> 00:05:10.626
My heart's beating way too fast.

00:05:15.182 --> 00:05:16.182
Calm down...

00:05:19.617 --> 00:05:20.617
Calm down...

00:05:34.297 --> 00:05:35.866
That hug...

00:05:35.866 --> 00:05:37.266
That breathing...

00:05:37.266 --> 00:05:39.293
It felt way too real.

00:05:39.293 --> 00:05:40.417
Oh my God!

00:05:51.966 --> 00:05:53.079
Where's your assignment?

00:05:56.300 --> 00:05:57.792
I'll go back and draw it now.

00:06:01.587 --> 00:06:02.587
What is that?

00:06:06.447 --> 00:06:07.520
Let me see.

00:06:07.521 --> 00:06:08.966
It's nothing.

00:06:10.133 --> 00:06:11.432
Miss.

00:06:17.216 --> 00:06:19.666
I haven't finished drawing yet.

00:06:26.266 --> 00:06:27.566
Remember to turn it in tomorrow.

00:06:29.973 --> 00:06:30.973
Okay.

00:06:31.466 --> 00:06:32.966
You're very quiet today.

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:34.800
Am I?

00:06:35.333 --> 00:06:37.461
No... not at all.

00:06:39.333 --> 00:06:42.966
Is the cat... doing okay?

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:45.900
Hurry back and draw.

00:06:47.565 --> 00:06:48.565
Oh.

00:06:52.500 --> 00:06:56.000
It seems, if she's just a little nice to me,

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:58.400
I get inexplicably happy.

00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:03.833
Could it be... that I've fallen for... my teacher?